arts.ttl: Toulouse predicted XI v Nantes: Le TéFéCé look to end run of defeats
arts.sum: FC Toulouse had looked as if they were finally ready to push on and become challengers for the European places when they defeated OGC Nice and Stade Brestois to start…

After starting the season in superb fashion, winning their opening two Ligue 1 games, it's been disappointing since then for Toulouse. They are current on a run of three straight losses in the league....
